title: The Streets - King George
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Israeli, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe with multiple locations. Contemporary atmosphere with free Wi-Fi. Marks the vegetarian/vegan choices on the menu. Has tofu dishes and bulghur patties as well vegetable dishes without meat. Large portions.
